Introduction

VERIVERY is a seven-member boy group under Jellyfish Entertainment. They made their official debut on January 9, 2019 with their first mini album VERI-US.

Verivery participated in the show "Road to Kingdom" with six other boy groups in March of 2020. They competed by taking on different performance challenges, showcasing their skills and charms. They ranked 5th by the end of the show.
